%A7%E8%B7%8C%E7%B4%8410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F202572%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2-bitcoin%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%25B4%258410&d=FiAKgoml5Zz3hpx%2Bxsr10f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8d2a9aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/202572/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2-bitcoin%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C%E7%B4%8410</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連最主要既function都無埋，你地覺得會彈得返上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819eb3af2b73c518915854c34db550406a2323b1","tid":714151,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://globalcoinreport.com/ripple-xrp-2019-price-prediction-10-usd-more-than-possible/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobalcoinreport.com%2Fripple-xrp-2019-price-prediction-10-usd-more-than-possible%2F&d=FiAKgoml5Zz3hpx%2Bxsr10f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cbe75bbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://globalcoinreport.com/ripple-xrp-2019-price-prediction-10-usd-more-than-possible/</a><br />\n<br />\n係真就好，哈哈"}]}